<section id="faq" class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-950 border-t border-gray-800">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">Everything you need to know about our services</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">What topics do you cover in your training sessions?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            <p>We cover a wide range of topics including security fundamentals, ethical hacking basics, secure coding practices, threat hunting, risk assessment, incident response, and current cybersecurity trends. All content is tailored to your audience's skill level and interests.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Can you deliver sessions virtually or in-person?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            <p>Yes! We offer both in-person and virtual sessions. Our virtual sessions are highly interactive using collaborative tools, live demos, and breakout exercises to maintain engagement.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">How long are typical training sessions?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            <p>Sessions typically range from 1-hour awareness talks to full-day workshops or multi-day training programs. We customize the duration based on your needs and objectives.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">What's the cost for a training session?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            <p>Pricing varies based on session length, format, customization needs, and group size. Contact us for a personalized quote. We offer special rates for educational institutions and non-profits.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Do participants need prior cybersecurity knowledge?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            <p>Not at all! We design sessions for all levels, from complete beginners to advanced learners. We'll work with you to understand your audience and tailor the content accordingly.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden">
        <details class="group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">How far in advance should we book?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-400 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-gray-400">
            <p>While we recommend booking 2-4 weeks in advance for optimal preparation, we can often accommodate last-minute requests depending on availability. Reach out and we'll do our best to work with your timeline.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
